  <description>
    <p>
      This is an unofficial package. Issues with it should not be reported to GDLauncher upstream!
    </p>
    <p>
      Main Features:
    </p>
    <p>
      Modern and easy to use UI
    </p>
    <p>
      Browse and Download CurseForge's Modpacks
    </p>
    <p>
      Support for Vanilla, Forge and Fabric
    </p>
    <p>
      Built in mods manager
    </p>
    <p>
      Auto java setup (Note that sometimes GDLauncher's java version can be behind and will require manual
      intervention: Simply right click on the instance you wish to use Flatpak Java for &gt; Click "Manage" &gt;
      Enable "Custom Java Path" &gt; And map the path to `/app/jre/bin/java`)
    </p>
  </description>

